INSERT INTO `jf_cms_content_ext` VALUES ('31', '六盘水,旅游,秀逗啊', '半方塘2天1夜休闲游\r\n炎炎夏日，烈日酷暑。“热情”好像永远都是夏天的别称，而节节攀升的气温仿佛正在不断暗示着炎热悄然而至。我们，是不是也该寻找一处心仪的避暑之地呢？\r\n来吧！天虹旅行社带你在这个夏天，沉迷在米箩的风景中，游走在巴朗河畔，邀上三五好友，携同家人孩子，摒弃城市的烦躁，彻底忘情于半方塘吧！', '<p class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">文章引自：（http://www.gzlps.gov.cn/cy/lyxd/yzld_35489/tjlyxl/201708/t20170808_1469055.html）</p><p class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">半方塘2天1夜休闲游</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">炎炎夏日，烈日酷暑。“热情”好像永远都是夏天的别称，而节节攀升的气温仿佛正在不断暗示着炎热悄然而至。我们，是不是也该寻找一处心仪的避暑之地呢？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">来吧！天虹旅行社带你在这个夏天，沉迷在米箩的风景中，游走在巴朗河畔，邀上三五好友，携同家人孩子，摒弃城市的烦躁，彻底忘情于半方塘吧！</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9000/xiudoua-cms/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170824/1503569916752091136.jpg\" title=\"1503569916752091136.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9000/xiudoua-cms/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170824/1503569916733036085.jpg\" title=\"1503569916733036085.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9000/xiudoua-cms/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170824/1503569916742003764.jpg\" title=\"1503569916742003764.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9000/xiudoua-cms/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170824/1503569932927011721.jpg\" title=\"1503569932927011721.jpg\" alt=\"W020170808523466015287.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">米箩景区·姚咏</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在这里，你可以暂时忘记自己的身份，穿梭在传统吊脚楼风格的建筑中，用心从每一个细节处进行探寻，彻底感受“慢生活”的惬意。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有动有静，方有乐趣，动静总相宜。如果布依族的“慢生活”能让你从紧张繁忙中解脱出来，那么水上乐园及水上拓展则是能够让你释放自我、激情嗨翻的娱乐项目。半方塘的水上乐园游乐设备自然不用多说，放眼望去，尽是各种惊险刺激项目应有尽有；而拓展项目则涵盖了各种锻炼、亲子、团体等各个方面。享受了“慢生活”之后，就让我们动起来嗨起来吧！</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9000/xiudoua-cms/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170824/1503569990996017725.jpg\" title=\"1503569990996017725.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9000/xiudoua-cms/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170824/1503569991011029216.jpg\" title=\"1503569991011029216.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9000/xiudoua-cms/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170824/1503569991022045620.jpg\" title=\"1503569991022045620.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9000/xiudoua-cms/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170824/1503569991027046410.jpg\" title=\"1503569991027046410.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9000/xiudoua-cms/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170824/1503569991039018402.jpg\" title=\"1503569991039018402.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">半方塘水上乐园·姚咏</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第一天早上10：00准时在六盘水凉都大剧院集合出发前往半方塘水上乐园，车程约50分钟</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">10：50到达半方塘</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">11：00游览半方塘景区，游览时间1小时</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">12：00中餐</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">13：00入住别墅酒店，酒店内包含麻将娱乐，其他项目凭自己喜欢自费，在景区内休闲娱乐至第二天下午14：00，返程回市区</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注：（所含费用：半方塘水上别墅风情酒店住宿一晚、水上乐园门票一张、一正餐、往返旅游大巴车费）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">惊爆价368/位，天天发团</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">乌蒙草原＋海坪彝族风情小镇一日游</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">乌蒙大草原是西南地区海拔最高，面积最大的高原草场之一。最高海拔为2857米，年平均气温为11.1℃，是一个夏日避暑的良好去处。这里有一望无际的独特高原草场，有万亩高原矮杜鹃林，有充满神奇色彩美丽动人的高山湖泊，有民族文化浓郁的彝族风情，有世界罕见的自然奇观——佛光，并融雄、奇、险、峻、幽于一身的牛棚梁子大山、八担山等。在乌蒙大草原立于山巅，看云涌苍崖，鹰翔蓝天，雾海漫漫，确有翻江倒海之壮阔，大江东去之豪迈。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9000/xiudoua-cms/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170824/1503570060480017126.jpg\" title=\"1503570060480017126.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9000/xiudoua-cms/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170824/1503570060493066729.jpg\" title=\"1503570060493066729.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9000/xiudoua-cms/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170824/1503570060508095709.jpg\" title=\"1503570060508095709.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9000/xiudoua-cms/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170824/1503570060510079057.jpg\" title=\"1503570060510079057.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">海坪彝族风情小镇·姚咏</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">早上7：50准时在六盘水凉都大剧院集合，8：00出发至乌蒙大草原，车程约1个半小时</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">9：30分到达乌蒙大草原，游览乌蒙大草原，游览时间2个半小时</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">12：00午餐</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">13：00集合乘车出发到海坪彝族景区，车程约1个半小时</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">14：30分到达海坪彝族景区，游览海坪彝景区，游览时间2小时</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">16：30结束愉快的行程，返程。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">惊爆价198/位，8月10号、14号、17号发团。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">北盘江游船＋北盘江第一桥一日游</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">北盘江大峡谷被誉为贵州峡谷之最，集峡谷风光之大成，以系列喀斯特及丹霞地貌大峡谷景观著称，是乌蒙山国家地质公园的核心区，集瀑布、石林、石洞、峰林等数十种自然风光于一体，峡谷内峰林怒拔，崇山峻岭依岸对列，河谷深切，相对高差在300－700米，水势变化无常，时急时缓，或跌落咆哮，颇为壮观。碧绿的江水缓缓流动，人行走在峡谷，不知不觉被感染，让你气定神闲，是个修身养性的世外桃源。徜徉在峡谷江面，既有“两岸猿声啼不住，轻舟已过万重山”的豪迈，亦有“春来江水绿如蓝”的婉约，它还是探险寻秘、体育健身的绝佳胜地。“静若处子，动若狡兔”是北盘江大峡谷的真实写照。</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">北盘江风光·张三都</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在北盘江大峡谷上还有著名的北盘江第一桥，北盘江第一桥创下一个世界第一，大桥全长1341.4米，桥面至谷底高差达565米，差不多相当于200层楼高，为目前“世界第一高桥”。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">北盘江第一桥·王远明</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">惊爆价238/位，周五发团。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">报名热线：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">贵州天虹旅行社：0858－8699666&nbsp;&nbsp; 　张 18985907922</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">麒麟社区服务部：杜 13116385466</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">六枝分公司：张 18785845561</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">投诉电话：13385585588</p><p><br/></p>', null, null, null);
